             was indicted for that <rs id="t18090215-73-off399" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090215-73-off399" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090215-73-off399" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>
               he on the <rs id="t18090215-73-cd400" type="crimeDate">9th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090215-73-off399 t18090215-73-cd400"></join>, was <rs id="t18090215-73-deflabel401" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090215-73-defend645 t18090215-73-deflabel401"></join> to 
                     
