                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090215-73-defend645 t18090215-73-punish405"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Baron Wood.</p>
